reviewText: Love these classics...I bought it for my parents, but, I also enjoyed it too!  The quality is very good.  Delivery and transaction was fast and easy:)
I will recommend it if people like good old black and white Mexican movies. With good sense of humor and like the actors.

It is a great movie for those of us who cherish & love our families.  I would recommend it to those who like movies that take place in the old Mexico and can understand the language well, otherwise you may miss some of the meanings
